      "message": "The list is relatively stable at this point. I\u0027m not sure adding such a test is worth the effort. If this list falls out of sync, Gazelle will either add invalid load() statements to our BUILD files, and/or generate rules that are not correctly imported. In both cases, the Bazel build would fail (i.e. Infra-PerCommit-Build-Bazel-* would turn red), and we would find out immediately.",
